Other Information

1. package.json - defines the application dependencies and other information.
2. www file - The application entry point. It sets up a node HTTP server with app set to 3000.
3. app.js - This file creates an express application object (named app, by convention), sets up the application with various settings and middleware, and then exports the app from the module.
